list.abstract: Library（英[ˈlaɪbrəri]，美[ˈlaɪbreri]），英语单词，作名词为图书馆；书房；书斋。短语搭配有library card（图书馆卡片，图书馆卡， 借书证）。例句为“I don't have a library card.（我没有借书证。）” Library相关近义词有athenaeum、bibliotheca。
《Library》是韩国女子演唱团体少女时代的小分队组合TaeTiSeo演唱的一首歌曲，收录于其首张迷你专辑《Twinkle》中，已于2012年4月30日发行。歌曲表现了一个女生以图书为背景对爱慕已久的男生的告白。具有轻节奏感的的旋律体现了少女心中的兴奋和倾心的爱恋。

yingyinNormal.en: So. How's the library? Museum. What happened to the library?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，图书馆还好吗？是博物馆。那图书馆呢？

yingyinNormal.en: I ripped this right out of a library book.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从图书馆的书里撕下的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my God! What were you doing in a library?
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，你去图书馆干什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Khadgar. I know you, from the library. You're Alodi?
yingyinNormal.zh: 卡德加。我知道你，在图书馆的时候，你是阿洛迪？

yingyinNormal.en: What kind of person is allergic to lobster? I guess the kind of person that works at a library. It's not a library.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁会对龙虾过敏？我猜是图书馆员。不是图书馆。

yingyinNormal.en: There never was a library. I mean there are libraries, its just that I never worked at one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有图书馆，是有图书馆，只不过我没在图书馆做过事。

yingyinNormal.en: This is why Hermione was in the library the day she was attacked.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是赫敏会在图书馆附近遭到攻击的原因。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Is it your book Daddy? It's a book I borrowed from the library.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这本是你的书吗，爸爸？这是我从图书馆里借来的一本书。

yingyinNormal.en: People here think excitement is a new "Please be quiet" Sign going up in the library.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里的人觉得兴奋就是图书馆里"保持安静"的标语。

yingyinNormal.en: Barbara Keeper. Eleanor Logan. Well then, let's go to the library and check.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是巴巴拉·门将。我是埃利诺·洛根。好的，我们去图书馆谈谈。

yingyinNormal.en: We're going to old school. You're gonna do your research at the New York public library.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要采取传统方式，你们必须去纽约公共图书馆做研究。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, I remember you telling me about that at the San Vicente branch of the public library.
yingyinNormal.zh: 知道，我记得你在公共图书馆圣文森特分馆跟我说过这事。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you know he once got an asthma attack from reading an old library book? You're kidding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道他有一次因为看图书馆的旧书引发哮喘吗？开玩笑的吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Unlike this house, the library will be completely quiet, so I can focus on my roommate selection.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不像我们家，图书馆会非常安静，我就可以专心选室友了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, okay. my weirdest place would have to be the women's room on the second floor of the New York City public library.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最奇怪的地方是在纽约市立图书馆二楼女厕。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, where have you guys been? The San Vicente branch of the public library, and then ice cream.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们上哪儿去了？公共图书馆圣文森特分馆，然后去吃了冰激凌。

yingyinNormal.en: It is the morning, Peppa and her family have come to the library. Wow, what's a lot of books.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是早上，佩奇和她的家人来到了图书馆。哇，这里有好多书啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Now who's being weirdly specific. Well, if you went to the library, why don't you have any books?
yingyinNormal.zh: 看现在是谁具体得诡异了，如果你们真去了图书馆为什么手里没书呢？

yingyinNormal.en: No, he had to settle for a presidential library. So it's been some time since you and I have had a chance to catch up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，只能委屈他拿一栋总统图书馆凑合了。我们都好久没聊聊了。

yingyinNormal.en: There are various social programs, cultural stuff I can sign you up for. And the public library is very close.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那有很多社区组织，我可以帮你报名参加各种文化活动。公共图书馆也很近。
